title: Back2Mad feat. Proxeeus & Neogoa Records
description:
Proxeeus and Anu at Neogoa Records talked about the new music, the upcoming anniversary party in Helsinki and plans for the future at Back2Mad show, streamed at Bassoradio on November 18th 2015.
